'''Ya̍p Â-lòi'''/Yap A-leu ([[Yang-vun]]: Yap Ah Loy; [[fan-ti chung-vun]]: 葉亞來) hai [[Kat-lun-po]] yit ge fui-fau-kung-sin. Hi hai Chung-kok [[Kóng-tûng]] [[sén|saang]] [[Fi-chiu-sṳ|Vai-chau]] [[Fi-yòng-khî|Vai-yong ki]] Chhau-chhong chan ke [[Hak-kâ|Hak-ka-ngin]]. Ya̍p Â-Lòi lang-du Kat-lun-po chik du [[1880]] nin wan chang yi [[Yîn-koet|Yang-kok]] chik-man ching-fu wai chi.

